This module is based on https://forge.puppetlabs.com/danleyden/ganglia . I added params.pp and changed some default value. It is hiera comapatiable.

include ganglia::client

Hiera data

ganglia::params::unicast_targets:
- ipaddress : ganglia_server
  port      : 8649


Limitation : server configuration is not tested 



Supports the installation of ganglia using puppet with multiclusters like described here:

http://sourceforge.net/apps/trac/ganglia/wiki/ganglia_quick_start

This module is published under the Apache 2.0 license - http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

